      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·國風·衛風·003.2</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">碩人.2</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>手如柔荑，膚如凝脂，領如蝤蠐，齒如瓠犀，螓首蛾眉，巧笑倩兮，美目盻兮。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Her fingers were like the blades of the young white-grass;
Her skin was like congealed ointment;
Her neck was like the tree-grub;
Her teeth were like melon seeds;
Her forehead cicada-like; her eyebrows like the silkworm moth;
What dimples, as she artfully smiled!
How beautiful were her clear black eyes!
O beautiful woman, so large and tall!</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="shijing__guofeng-weifeng-003__003__zhwikisource-20260530__legge-sheking-1871-ocr">
